  RS-tab  RS-q    RS-w    RS-e    RS-r    RS-t    RS-y    RS-u    RS-i    RS-o    RS-p    RS-[    RS-]    RS-ret   RS-del  RS-end  RS-pgdn  RS-kp7  RS-kp8  RS-kp9  RS-kp+
  del     RS-a    RS-s    RS-d    RS-f    RS-g    RS-h    RS-j    RS-k    RS-l    RS-;    RS-'    RS-\                                      RS-kp4  RS-kp5  RS-kp6
  _       RS-lsgt RS-z    RS-x    RS-c    RS-v    RS-b    RS-n    RS-m    RS-,    RS-.    RS-/            _                RS-up            RS-kp1  RS-kp2  RS-kp3  RS-kprt
