  M-tab  M-q    M-w    M-e    M-r    M-t    M-y    home   up     end    pgup   M-[    M-]    M-ret   M-del  M-end  M-pgdn  M-kp7  M-kp8  M-kp9  M-kp+
  M-caps M-a    M-s    M-d    M-f    M-g    M-h    left   down   right  pgdn   M-'    M-\                                  M-kp4  M-kp5  M-kp6
